job.title: HPAS Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 16 Vacancy in Himachal Pradesh
job.body:
Total vacancies:16

Name of the Posts:

  • HP Administrative Services - 08
  • District Controller, FCS&CA, (UR) - 01
  • HP Police Services - 04
  • Tehsildar - 01
  • Assistant Registrar (UR) - 02

Description

New State Government Jobs for Graduates have been published by Himachal Pradesh Public Service Commission for the posts of Administrative. If you are searching for a government job in Himachal Pradesh then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the post of Administrative, from 19-05-2021, and till 22-06-2021 at 11:59 PM. If you are interested in all these posts and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee

  • The mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for General & Candidates of Other States is only Rs. 400/-.
  • The application fee for SC/ ST/ OBC of HP State is only Rs. 100/-.
  • No application fee for ex-serviceman.

Educational qualification:

To apply for Administrative vacancies in Himachal Pradesh, your Graduation must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply for these posts is 19-05-2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these posts is 22-06-2021

Age Limit Criteria

For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35  years old. 

HPAS Administrative Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Himachal Pradesh Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms.

How to apply for HPAS Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Administrative. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of HPAS and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by HPAS.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
